name: Frank Danny
description: I’m an honest, loyal, fun-loving, intelligent, deep thinking, giving person. I am also passionate about my career, personal goals and seeing my dreams come true. I am also a believer in Christian way, and there is a romantic in me that enjoys being spontaneous and doing the little things that matter. For fun, I enjoy traveling, performing arts, cooking, feature films and art galleries. Having a glass of wine, watching sunset, and spending time with friends.
